A [[Main/en/Advanced Settings|setting]] that displays the current vehicle speed in the vehicle information window.

== Description ==
Once this patch is activated, you'll know at any time how fast your vehicle is moving. The speed will be either displayed in km/h or mph, depending on your settings. You can change the distance units in the [[Main/en/Game options window]].

== Use ==
This feature is enabled by default. You can disable it through the [[Main/en/Advanced Settings/Interface#Show vehicle speed in status bar|configure patches -> interface]] window or use the following syntax in [[Main/en/openttd.cfg]]:

<pre>
[patches]
vehicle_speed = false
</pre>
